headline: DuPont™ IntegraTec™ XTP 100 IG Ultrafiltration Modules Now Available Globally
summary: DuPont today announced that DuPont™ IntegraTec™ XTP 100 IG ultrafiltration modules are now available globally. A groundbreaking solution powered by innovative PVDF hollow fiber technology, designed specifically for industrial applications, these modules present a significant advancement in process and wastewater management.
